      "content": "that's a good start. it captures the tone well. could you expand on the part about the tribes being \"chaotic\"? maybe have him describe how they look or how they act compared to how a \"proper\" society should function. make it feel more descriptive and visceral so the audience can really see why he thinks they need his help.",
